sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant DB

    User->>Frontend: Add item (qty)
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/products/:id
    Backend->>DB: Find product
    DB-->>Backend: Product (stock, price)
    alt In stock
        Frontend-->>User: Item added to cart
    else Out of stock
        Frontend-->>User: Show error
    end

    User->>Frontend: Update qty / Remove item
    Frontend-->>User: Cart totals updated
